# 05-state-management-rules.mdc

---
description: State ownership rules
globs:
- "**/*.dart"
---

Classify state:

UI State:
- Loading
- Dialog visibility
- Tabs
- Temporary interaction

Session State:
- Authentication
- User identity
- Permissions

Domain State:
- Providers
- Listings
- Bookings
- Reviews

Remote State:
- Backend synchronized data

Persistent State:
- Preferences
- Settings

Every state variable must have clear ownership.
